Module kline.qkmii.inventorymgmtsystem
Package kline.qkmii.inventorymgmtsystem.util

Class TextFieldContainer

java.lang.Object
kline.qkmii.inventorymgmtsystem.util.TextFieldContainer
public class TextFieldContainer extends Object
A C++-style struct. Holds components of a typical text field form (exempt of the label):
  • The text field box
  • The validation text below the box
The InputType is a property that explicitly declares the type of data the text field form should take. Validations are handled by the static helper class ErrorHandler.
Author:
Timothy Albert Kline
